=== Nicer HTML Font ===
Contributors: jmdodd
Tags: 
Requires at least: 
Tested up to: 3.2.1
Stable tag: 0.1

Revert the textarea font in the HTML Editor from monospace to the WP3.1 
sans-serif stack.

== Description ==

Nicer HTML Font is used to revert the HTML Editor textarea font from the 
hard-to-read monospace font stack to the sans-serif font stack from WP3.1.

Development funded, in part, by Ariel Meadow Stallings and the Offbeat Empire.

== Installation ==

1. Upload the directory `shadow-screen-options` and its contents to the 
`/wp-content/plugins/` directory.
1. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress.

